Body:
Description: Hello Team,

One of our customers require bulk unisntallation script.

Kindly do the needful.
What We've Learned Updated: Client would like to know if there is some sort of script they could apply in their environment so they could perform a bulk uninstall of the EPP client.

Next Steps Updated: We do have a script but that is only for installation deployments. If the client wants to uninstall the EPP, they can do it directly through the console->System Config->Client uninstallation and they can select multiple devices at once to uninstall. Will follow up with them to gather more details.

What We've Learned Updated: Client got back stating they can't use the uninstall option from the console for some reason.
Asked for more details to investigate.
Next Steps Updated: Sent mail explaining how to do it and to provide more details with relevant screenshots. Will wait for their response.
